source.name: The Hordeum Toolbox
source.description: THT hosts data generated by the Barley Coordinated Agricultural Project (CAP), and contains SNP, phenotypic, and pedigree data from breeding germplasm in the Barley CAP. This effort is now being carried forward as part of the Triticeae CAP in the T3 databases.
